  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators evaluate if intravenously applied THC (Cannabis) reduces postoperative
      Nausea and vomiting. THC will be given during anesthesia before emergence. We measure how
      long and how effective it reduces PONV
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
